// Smoke project for lake-house dep injection.
//
// `lake.house` lists `dep "demo-lib" "0.0.1" path "deps/demo-lib"`,
// so `house build` sets DEMO_LIB_PATH=<...>/deps/demo-lib before
// invoking lakec, and the frontend's loader resolves the import
// below through that env var (see lake-frontend/src/loader.rs).

+demo_lib.greet.{ hello }

main is {
  _ -> { hello() }
}
